   * Add github actions
     - Add roscpp as CATKIN_DEPENDS
     - Use the .ci.rosinstall to install dependencies
     - Move rosinstall for testing to typical place for industrial-ci
     - Update ci badges to GHA
     - Remove travis
   * Contributors: JeroenDM, Simon Schmeisser
